### Create Session
POST http://localhost:2323/sessions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "work_dir": "/tmp/workspace"
}

### List All Sessions
GET http://localhost:2323/sessions

### Get Session by ID
GET http://localhost:2323/sessions/{{session_id}}

### Update Session
PUT http://localhost:2323/sessions/{{session_id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "work_dir": "/home/user/projects"
}

### Delete Session
DELETE http://localhost:2323/sessions/{{session_id}}

### Send Message to Session
POST http://localhost:2323/sessions/{{session_id}}/message
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "agent_id": "{{agent_id}}",
  "prompt": "Write a hello world program in Python"
}

### Send Message with Streaming
POST http://localhost:2323/sessions/{{session_id}}/message/stream
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "agent_id": "{{agent_id}}",
  "prompt": "Explain how this codebase works"
}
